page.title: 18My hobbies, Kesgrave
page.content:
My hobbies are dancing, swimming and Cubs. My favouite hobby is dancing because I am fairly good. I go to the Ipswich School Of Dancing and I have 64 medals, trophies, cups and shields, and a big scroll made of wood. I compete in International and Open competitions in places like Norwich, Hammersmith, Crystal Palace and The Albert Hall.
I have been dancing for about 3 years and during that time I have had three partners. I went to two other dancing schools before the one I go to now. The Ipswich School Of Dancing has not been beaten in competitions for 5 years.
